node.title: Body recovered from Clutha River believed to be missing man
node.description: Police officers searching for a missing man in Central Otago have recovered a body from the Clutha River.
node.content:
["Police officers searching for a missing man in Central Otago have recovered a body from the Clutha River.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Members of the public saw the body in the river near Teviot yesterday afternoon.", "Police said while a post-mortem and formal identification was yet to be completed, they believe it's missing 20-year-old Rian Williamson.", "He was last seen in nearby Roxburgh late on 2 February."]
